      En savoir plus sur http://www.lesechos.fr/?orH8mmTt5FFPLVix.99
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
      <h1>Welcome!</h1>

      <h2>This is the homepage</h2>

      <p>
        <%= link_to 'Liste des articles', articles_path %>
        <%= link_to 'Créer un article', new_article_path %>
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <%= link_to 'Editer le profil', edit_user_registration_path %>
        <% end %>
      </p>

      <p>
        Thanks to the <a href="https://github.com/thoughtbot/high_voltage">high_voltage</a>
